<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Date converts incorrectly some dates using user-specified format. This happens only by the last day of some years (2007,2008,2011,2012,2013)</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$date = new Zend_Date('31.12.2007', 'dd.MM.YYYY');
echo $date; // Dec 31, 2007 12:00:00 AM
echo $date-&gt;get(Zend_Date::ISO_8601); // 2007-12-31T00:00:00+01:00
echo $date-&gt;toString('YYYY-MM-dd'); // 2008-12-31
</code></pre>

